<!DOCTYPE en-note SYSTEM "http://xml.evernote.com/pub/enml2.dtd"><en-note><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">How to Login to a Database</span></div><div><br /></div><div>=&gt; mysql -u khasanov -h 192.168.100.250 -p</div><div>( give your password)</div><div>mysql&gt; </div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">Database Users</span></div><div><br /></div><div># Show all users in the Database:</div><div>=&gt; SELECT User, Host, Password FROM mysql.user;</div><div><br /></div><div># To CREATE a User:</div><div>=&gt; CREATE User ‘TestUser’@‘localhost’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘testuser_password’;</div><div><br /></div><div># To DELETE a User:</div><div>=&gt; DROP User ‘TestUser’@‘localhost’;</div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">Creating Databases</span></div><div><br /></div><div># To create a Database:</div><div>=&gt; CREATE DATABASE Test.db;</div><div><br /></div><div># To use the Database:</div><div>=&gt; USE Test.db</div><div><br /></div><div># To drop a Database:</div><div>=&gt; DROP DATABASE Test.db;</div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold;">Database Privileges</span></div><div><br /></div><div># To grant all the privileges to “khasanov” on the local machine:</div><div>=&gt; GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO ‘khasanov’@‘localhost’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘his-password’;</div><div>Note: This will restrict the user to the local machine. He might have a different privileges depend</div><div>          on where he is coming from ( i.e. Is he using a remotely? )</div><div><br /></div><div># If the user is coming from the remote IP Address and you want to grant him the above privileges:</div><div>=&gt; GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO ‘khasanov’@‘IP_Address’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘his-password’;</div><div><br /></div><div># If you wnat the user login from any where, use the “%” instead of the IP Address:</div><div>=&gt; GRANT ALL PRIVILEGES ON *.* TO ‘khasanov’@‘%’ IDENTIFIED BY ‘his-password’;</div><div><br /></div><div>=&gt; FLUSH PRIVILEGES;</div><div>=&gt; SHOW GRANTS for ‘khasanov’@‘localhost’;</div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 18px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">How To Back Up and Restoring a Database?</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># In this example we are going to back up the ownCloud DB running in the FreeBSD Server</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># The name of the databse: kfh_icloud_db</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># User name: khasanov</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># Password: OldBASE</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># The new location: MAC OS X Server</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"># The new database name: icloud_db</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Step 1. Login to the FreeBSD server using the SSH </span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">        =&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">ssh</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(3, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">khasanov</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">@</span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 32, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">10.10.10.210</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Step 2. Backup the database using the "mysqldump" command:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">=&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mysqldump -u</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(3, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">khasanov</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">-p</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 59, 164); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">kfh_icloud_db</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 156, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">icloud_db.sql</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">        # This file will contain all the SQL statements needed to re-create the database</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Step 3. Login the MAC OS X Server and copy the backup file :</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">           =&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">scp</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(3, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">khasanov</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">@</span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(167, 59, 164); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">10.10.10.210</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">:</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">~/</span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 156, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">icloud_db.sql</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">~/tmp</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">           =&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">cd ~/tmp</span></div><div><br /></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Step 4. Create a database on MAC OS X Server:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">          =&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> mysql -u </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(3, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">khasanov</span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(3, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">-p</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">         </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 161, 164); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mysql&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">CREATE DATABASE</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 101, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">icloud_db</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">;</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">          </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 161, 164); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mysql&gt;</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">quit</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">;</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">Step 5. Restore the database:</span></div><div><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">          =&gt; </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">mysql -u</span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> </span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(3, 82, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;">khasanov </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">-p</span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(255, 101, 255); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> icloud_db </span><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: normal;">&lt;</span><span style="font-size: 12px; color: rgb(0, 156, 0); font-family: Helvetica; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: normal;"> icloud_db.sql</span></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div><div><br /></div></en-note>